### =========================================================================
### KONFIGURASI VARIABEL
### =========================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = Fn44aTZsuZRxlKju1u1pPVVgv1z9ksCVRey61BYMa66fc16a

### =========================================================================
### 1. AUTENTIKASI (PINTU MASUK)
### =========================================================================

### Register User Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Fajar Bagas",
    "email": "fajar2@test.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

### Login (Ambil Token di sini)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "email": "bagas@test.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Logout (Hapus Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### =========================================================================
### 2. MANAJEMEN KATEGORI
### =========================================================================

### Ambil Semua Kategori Milik User
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Tambah Kategori Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Jalan"
}

### Update Nama Kategori (Ganti {id} dengan ID asli)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Kuliner & Jajan"
}

### Hapus Kategori
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### =========================================================================
### 3. MANAJEMEN TRANSAKSI
### =========================================================================

### Ambil Semua Riwayat Transaksi
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Tambah Transaksi Baru (Ganti category_id sesuai ID yang ada)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "amount": 5000,
    "category_id": 3,
    "description": "Beli minum",
    "type": "expense"
}

### Detail Satu Transaksi
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Update Transaksi
PATCH  {{baseUrl}}/transactions/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "amount": 55000,
    "category_id": 2,
    "description": "Nasi Padang + Es Jeruk",
    "type": "expense"
}

### Hapus Transaksi
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### =========================================================================
### 4. FITUR RINGKASAN (SUMMARY)
### =========================================================================

### Lihat Total Saldo, Income, dan Expense
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json